=============================================================================
    UUP-MAIL - Mail template and composing library for PHP
=============================================================================

The uup-mail library provides a mail template and composer library for formatting
mail messages. The main focus is on the composition. All message sending is 
delegated to the swift-mailer library.

This library is not designed to be used as a component library. Instead, it was
designed with inheritance in mind. Create your own mail message classes (one for 
each particular kind of message) derived from class MessageComposer and implement 
the MessageCreator interface:

// 
// Example:
// 
class ConfirmSubscriptionMessage extends MessageComposer implements MessageCreator
{
        public function __construct()
        {
                parent::__construct(_("Confirm Subscription", _("...")));
                // ... create section headers with content.
        }

        public function create($formatter) 
        {
                return new Message($this, $formatter);  // Swift_Message
        }
}

$composer = new ConfirmSubscriptionMessage();
$message  = $composer->create($formatter);
$mailer->send($message);

